title: Detour to Clit Town
description:
Lauren reveals whether or not she'd sell feet pics before taking a detour to Clit Town. Jeremy talks about his jobs growing up and teaching music. Lauren & Jeremy discuss the privilege of growing up middle class and how they handle money inside of their relationship.
